## 4. Frontend Implementation

### 4.1 Pages (8 total)

| Page | File | Key Features |
|------|------|-------------|
| Dashboard | [DashboardPage.tsx](file:///w:/level%203/Software/System/src/pages/DashboardPage.tsx) | KPIs, low-stock alerts, recent transactions, system overview |
| Products | [ProductsPage.tsx](file:///w:/level%203/Software/System/src/pages/ProductsPage.tsx) | CRUD, search/filter by category/supplier, SKU & barcode |
| Stock | [StockPage.tsx](file:///w:/level%203/Software/System/src/pages/StockPage.tsx) | Branch selector, live quantities, quick adjust modal |
| Orders | [OrdersPage.tsx](file:///w:/level%203/Software/System/src/pages/OrdersPage.tsx) | Purchase/Sale tabs, line items, status workflow |
| Branches | [BranchesPage.tsx](file:///w:/level%203/Software/System/src/pages/BranchesPage.tsx) | CRUD branches, toggle active/inactive |
| Users | [UsersPage.tsx](file:///w:/level%203/Software/System/src/pages/UsersPage.tsx) | List users, assign roles and branches |
| Reports | [ReportsPage.tsx](file:///w:/level%203/Software/System/src/pages/ReportsPage.tsx) | Date range filters, stock movement, export PDF/CSV |
| 404 | [NotFoundPage.tsx](file:///w:/level%203/Software/System/src/pages/NotFoundPage.tsx) | Error boundary for invalid routes |

### 4.2 Shared Components

| Component | Purpose |
|-----------|---------|
| [DataTable.tsx](file:///w:/level%203/Software/System/src/components/DataTable.tsx) | Reusable data table with sorting, filtering, pagination |
| [CommandPalette.tsx](file:///w:/level%203/Software/System/src/components/CommandPalette.tsx) | Global search/command palette (⌘+K) |
| [TransferStockModal.tsx](file:///w:/level%203/Software/System/src/components/TransferStockModal.tsx) | Inter-branch stock transfer dialog |
| Layout (Header, Sidebar) | Application shell with navigation |
| UI Primitives | Button, Input, Table, Dropdown, Popover |

### 4.3 Key Design Patterns

- **Lazy loading**: All route pages use `React.lazy()` with `Suspense` for code splitting
- **Server state**: TanStack Query manages all API data with 5-minute stale time and 2 retries
- **Routing**: React Router v7 `createBrowserRouter` with nested layout routes
- **API client**: Centralized Axios instance in [src/api/client.ts](file:///w:/level%203/Software/System/src/api/client.ts)

