## 6. Database Schema

### 6.1 Tables (10 total)

```mermaid
erDiagram
    categories ||--o{ products : "belongs_to"
    suppliers ||--o{ products : "supplies"
    products ||--o{ stock_levels : "tracked_at"
    branches ||--o{ stock_levels : "holds"
    stock_levels ||--o{ stock_transactions : "logs"
    products ||--o{ order_items : "ordered"
    orders ||--o{ order_items : "contains"
    orders }o--|| branches : "placed_at"
    orders }o--o| suppliers : "from"
    profiles }o--|| branches : "assigned_to"
```

### 6.2 Key Security Features

| Feature | Details |
|---------|---------|
| **Row-Level Security** | Enabled on all 10 tables with 32 policies |
| **Deny-by-Default** | Unauthorized operations are silently rejected |
| **Branch Isolation** | Staff users see only their assigned branch's data |
| **Immutable Audit Log** | `stock_transactions` — client-side writes are blocked |
| **Atomic Stock Updates** | `adjust_stock_level()` RPC with `SELECT ... FOR UPDATE` |
| **Non-negative Constraint** | `CHECK (quantity >= 0)` on [stock_levels](file:///w:/level%203/Software/System/backend/app/routers/stock.py#10-19) |

### 6.3 RBAC Permissions Matrix

| Capability | Admin | Manager | Staff |
|------------|:-----:|:-------:|:-----:|
| View Dashboard | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ |
| Manage Products | ✅ | ✅ | ❌ |
| Quick Stock Adjustment | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ (own branch) |
| Create / Approve Orders | ✅ | ✅ | ❌ |
| Manage Branches | ✅ | ❌ | ❌ |
| Manage Users & Roles | ✅ | ❌ | ❌ |
| Export Reports | ✅ | ✅ | ❌ |
| View Own Branch Stock | ✅ | ✅ | ✅ |

### 6.4 Realtime Subscriptions

| Table | Event | Frontend Use Case |
|-------|-------|-------------------|
| `notifications` | `INSERT` | Push toast alerts for low-stock warnings |
| [stock_levels](file:///w:/level%203/Software/System/backend/app/routers/stock.py#10-19) | `UPDATE` | Live dashboard inventory updates |

