## 7. Deployment & Configuration

### 7.1 Environment Variables

| Variable | Purpose |
|----------|---------|
| `SUPABASE_URL` | Supabase project URL |
| `SUPABASE_ANON_KEY` | Public API key (RLS-enforced) |
| `SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY` | Admin key (bypasses RLS) |
| `DATABASE_URL` | Direct PostgreSQL connection string |

### 7.2 Running the System

| Component | Command |
|-----------|---------|
| Frontend (dev) | `npm run dev` |
| Frontend (build) | `npm run build` |
| Backend (dev) | `uvicorn app.main:app --reload` |
| Database seed | `python seed_db.py` |

### 7.3 Deployment Targets

- **Frontend**: Vercel (configured via [vercel.json](file:///w:/level%203/Software/System/vercel.json))
- **Backend**: Any Python hosting (Docker-ready)
- **Database**: Supabase managed PostgreSQL

