## 9. Migration History

A total of **22 database migrations** have been successfully applied:

| Phase | Count | Description |
|-------|-------|-------------|
| Extensions & Enums | 2 | `uuid-ossp`, `pgcrypto`, 4 enum types |
| Core Tables | 8 | All 10 tables with constraints, indexes, FK relations |
| Functions & Triggers | 2 | `update_timestamp()` trigger, `adjust_stock_level()` RPC |
| RLS Policies | 8 | 32 policies across all tables |
| Security Hardening | 1 | Search-path injection prevention |
| Realtime | 1 | `notifications` and [stock_levels](file:///w:/level%203/Software/System/backend/app/routers/stock.py#10-19) publications |

